<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <title>About Connect Book</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f4f7f6;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
        }

        .about-container {
            margin-top: 5rem;
            margin-bottom: 5rem;
        }

        .card {
            margin: 0 auto;
            max-width: 800px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .card-header {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 2rem;
            border: none;
        }

        .card-body {
            padding: 3rem;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .section-title {
            color: #007bff;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #eef2f7;
            padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .developer-badge {
            background-color: #eef2f7;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            border-left: 5px solid #007bff;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 0;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container about-container">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header text-center">
                <h2>About Connect Book</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <p class="lead text-center">
                    Connect Book is a professional-grade facility management solution designed to streamline resource allocation and scheduling.
                </p>

                <h5 class="section-title">The Project Vision</h5>
                <p>
                    This system was developed to modernize the reservation experience, replacing manual logs and traditional queuing with a real-time, digital environment. Connect Book ensures that facilities are managed efficiently, providing users with instant access to availability and secure booking tools.
                </p>

                <h5 class="section-title">Key Capabilities</h5>
                <p>
                    Built with a focus on reliability and user experience, the system automates complex scheduling tasks, prevents double-bookings, and provides a centralized dashboard for facility oversight.
                </p>

                <div class="developer-badge">
                    <h5 class="mb-2">Lead Engineer</h5>
                    <p class="mb-0"><strong>Lindele Xolani Nyambe</strong></p>
                    <p class="small text-muted">Full-Stack Software Developer</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
